{"tid":633953,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"lemon tree呢首歌背後嘅恐怖故事","createTime":"2018-04-18T18:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T19:45:32.000Z","uid":180486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c437cf3725ac4d48b06d2e4c31f935c7987463","tid":633953,"uid":180486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:29:09.000Z","msg":"我以前聽過一個版本，係話個男仔嘅女朋友發生車禍，撞咗落棵檸檬樹度死咗，搞到我聽親呢首歌都有陰影。<br />\n<br />\n睇下歌詞又覺得幾似：<br />\nI'm sitting here in the boring room<br />\nIt's just another rainy Sunday afternoon<br />\nI'm wasting my time<br />\nI got nothing to do<br />\nI'm hanging around<br />\nI'm waiting for you<br />\nBut nothing ever happens and I wonder<br />\nI'm driving around in my car<br />\nI'm driving too fast<br />\nI'm driving too far<br />\nI'd like to change my point of view<br />\nI feel so lonely<br />\nI'm waiting for you<br />\nBut nothing ever happens and I wonder<br />\nI wonder how<br />\nI wonder why<br />\nYesterday you told me 'bout the blue blue sky<br />\nAnd all that I can see is just a yellow lemon-tree<br />\nI'm turning my head up and down<br />\nI'm turning turning turning turning turning around<br />\nAnd all that I can see is just another lemon-tree...<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以分析下？"},{"pid":"1aff5a8f7bdf18526ac53eb470908654f117989d","tid":633953,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:36:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"489a32cb38df04b0770cebe546838034ff215e33","tid":633953,"uid":54181,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:43:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e73966bc0f6d5d26258caae7069a334cadc1c0a0","tid":633953,"uid":31475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:43:58.000Z","msg":"點解"},{"pid":"d6ea3a1746f6e60b7ef4bc58f6a35d5e187342fe","tid":633953,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"489a32cb38df04b0770cebe546838034ff215e33","tid":633953,"uid":54181,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:43:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:56:38.000Z","msg":"作者想表達：冇呀，啱音同搵食囉..."},{"pid":"4e1b4c5ea000e4b887cba9b1e5060424e4f2e395","tid":633953,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:15:08.000Z","msg":"I wonder how~ i wonder why<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有聲<br />\n仲有一首咩season in the sun都話係恐怖歌"},{"pid":"e8c67ebdb2e3fc50050e095020d6cb6e151dcc42","tid":633953,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:22:01.000Z","msg":"我是渣渣灰"},{"pid":"0f682494c3037dce04af354c59e0452fb3803c83","tid":633953,"uid":56018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e1b4c5ea000e4b887cba9b1e5060424e4f2e395","tid":633953,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:15:08.000Z","msg":"I wonder how~ i wonder why<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有聲<br />\n仲有一首咩season in the sun都話係恐怖歌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:25:19.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下seasons in the sun<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66c09cb7bcc8b919ee36497fd64dc6bb7d22197","tid":633953,"uid":180486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:30:28.000Z","msg":"有幾個地方我覺得幾可疑：<br />\n<br />\nIt's just another rainy Sunday afternoon<br />\nAnother？咁之前嗰個rainy Sunday afternoon發生咗咩事？會唔會佢女友撞車同落雨有關？<br />\n<br />\nI'm hanging around<br />\nI'm waiting for you<br />\nBut nothing ever happens and I wonder<br />\n條女始終無出現嘅原因係咩？<br />\n<br />\nI'm driving around in my car<br />\nI'm driving too fast<br />\nI'm driving too far<br />\nI'd like to change my point of view<br />\nI feel so lonely<br />\nI'm waiting for you<br />\n呢度最可疑，失戀或者等唔到條女都唔使開快車掛？傷心到咁？但如果係上面個講法成件事就合理好多。<br />\n<br />\nYesterday you told me 'bout the blue blue sky<br />\nAnd all that I can see is just a yellow lemon-tree<br />\n諗返起條女講嘅嘢，但成個腦都係檸檬樹。<br />\n<br />\nI'm turning my head up and down<br />\nI'm turning turning turning turning turning around<br />\nAnd all that I can see is just another lemon-tree<br />\n已經崩潰咗，不斷想起檸檬樹。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個講法係我之前唔記得係邊度睇過，首歌俾人感覺都幾輕快，但如果仔細留意啲歌詞，會發現唔知點解咁悲慘，主角係抑鬱同埋崩潰狀態，而且檸檬樹嗰part又好奇怪。"},{"pid":"d16613cdf2e563d26980de28e08637987fe2fb2b","tid":633953,"uid":136017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:32:15.000Z","msg":"考評局咩"},{"pid":"d5fea8ab0bf63f031e6b638805f80652f2e33223","tid":633953,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f682494c3037dce04af354c59e0452fb3803c83","tid":633953,"uid":56018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e1b4c5ea000e4b887cba9b1e5060424e4f2e395","tid":633953,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:15:08.000Z","msg":"I wonder how~ i wonder why<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有聲<br />\n仲有一首咩season in the sun都話係恐怖歌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:25:19.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下seasons in the sun<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:33:31.000Z","msg":"我唔記得啦 好細個聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要foxy down<br />\n話有恐怖野<br />\n<br />\n歌詞係咩byebye papa is time to die(記錯勿屌)"},{"pid":"7bbfd53b4a646a20590657879a1b235043a6f01b","tid":633953,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5fea8ab0bf63f031e6b638805f80652f2e33223","tid":633953,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f682494c3037dce04af354c59e0452fb3803c83","tid":633953,"uid":56018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e1b4c5ea000e4b887cba9b1e5060424e4f2e395","tid":633953,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:15:08.000Z","msg":"I wonder how~ i wonder why<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有聲<br />\n仲有一首咩season in the sun都話係恐怖歌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:25