\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個超鍾意聽seasons in the sun.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:45:32.000Z","msg":"But the hills that we climbed were just seasons out of time<br />\nBut the stars we could reach were just starfishes on the beach<br />\n呢句真。<br />\n無嘢留得低，無嘢有意義。"}]}